Package: scim-sunpinyin
Architecture: any
Section: utils
Depends: scim, ${sunpinyin-data-depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Sunpinyin input method of Chinese Language Engine for SCIM
 Sunpinyin is an SLM based input method engine developed by Sun.
 .
 This package contains SunPinyin input method for SCIM.

Package: iiimf-le-sunpinyin-chinese
Section: text
Architecture: any
Depends: iiimf-server, iiimf-le-sun-simplified-chinese, ${sunpinyin-data-depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Sunpinyin input method of Chinese Language Engine for iiimf-server
 Sunpinyin is an SLM based input method engine developed by Sun.
 .
 This package contains Sunpinyin input method of Chinese Language Engine for 
 Internet/Intranet Input Method.

Package: sunpinyin-data-le
Architecture: all
Enhances: scim-sunpinyin, iiimf-le-sunpinyin-chinese
Conflicts: sunpinyin-data-be
Description: Little-endian data file for SunPinyin input method engine
 Sunpinyin is an SLM based input method engine developed by Sun.
 .
 This package contains necessary lexicon data and its index data files
 needed for the sunpinyin input methods on little endian architectures.

Package: sunpinyin-data-be
Architecture: all
Enhances: scim-sunpinyin, iiimf-le-sunpinyin-chinese
Conflicts: sunpinyin-data-le
Description: Big-endian data file for SunPinyin input method engine
 Sunpinyin is an SLM based input method engine developed by Sun.
 .
 This package contains necessary lexicon data and its index data files
 needed for the sunpinyin input methods on big endian architectures.
